The Postmaster of Mafdet maintains an open expedition commission for a complete navigation survey of the Southern Pyramid. The pyramid's internal layout is poorly documented compared to its northern counterpart, and crews operating in the area have reported navigating from incomplete records. Chart every accessible chamber, corridor, and access route within the Southern Pyramid and return with a full survey record.
Your Southern Pyramid survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority expedition archive. The postmaster has closed the open commission and the completed record has been added to the expedition reference files alongside the Northern Pyramid documentation.
